To build the docker image, please run in this directory:

# docker build -t testbamboo .


To execute the docker image under unix, please create local directory ./bamboo_home and run:

# docker run -d -v $(pwd)/bamboo_home:/var/atlassian/application-data/bamboo --name="bamboo" --init -p 54663:54663 -p 8085:8085 testbamboo

To stop the image enter

# docker stop bamboo

To restart the image enter

# docker restart bamboo